### Introduction

Welcome to the Hackney Allotments Society's website ("Website"). We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your personal information in compliance with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and other applicable data protection laws.

### Information we collect

We may collect and process the following categories of personal information:<br>
- Personal Identification Information: This includes your name, contact details (such as email address, phone number, and postal address), and other information you provide when contacting us, registering for events, or becoming a member.<br>
- Payment Information: When you make payments for memberships or events, we may collect financial information to process transactions securely.<br>
- Website Usage Data: We collect data about your interactions with our Website, such as pages visited, time spent on the site, and IP address. This information helps us understand how you use our services and improve our Website.<br>
- Communications: We may store records of your interactions with us, including emails and other forms of communication, to provide better customer service and maintain accurate records.<br>

### How we use your information

We use your personal information for the following purposes:<br>
- Membership and Services: To manage your membership, provide requested services, and communicate with you about relevant activities and events.<br>
- Payment Processing: To process payments for memberships, events, or donations securely and efficiently.<br>
- Communication: To respond to your inquiries, provide information about our activities, and send you relevant updates via email or other communication channels.<br>
- Website Improvement: To analyze usage patterns, troubleshoot technical issues, and enhance the functionality and content of our Website.<br>
- Legal and Regulatory Compliance: To comply with applicable laws, regulations, and legal processes.<br>

